            </p>
            <div class="mt-8 flex space-x-4">
              <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700">
                Começar análise
              </a>
              <%= link_to "Conversor de Imagens", image_converters_path, class: "inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm text-base font-medium rounded-md text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50" %>
